- They're really, really cute.
- Listen, Hen. We're not having...

30
00:03:43,892 --> 00:03:46,061
- Tell him. It's the dog thing again.
- But why, Dad?

31
00:03:46,144 --> 00:03:48,438
We can't have a dog
because, as I've said before,

32
00:03:48,522 --> 00:03:50,357
all dogs make my throat close up,

33
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,609
so no air gets to my lungs,
which makes me die.

34
00:03:52,692 --> 00:03:54,361
So, it's undesirable.

35
00:03:54,444 --> 00:03:55,695
- But...
- Think of another pet.

36
00:03:55,779 --> 00:03:57,823
You can have a cat or a hamster.

37
00:03:57,906 --> 00:03:59,699
I don't know what kids have these days.

38
00:03:59,783 --> 00:04:01,326
Have a vampire bat.

39
00:04:03,203 --> 00:04:05,664
- Is that a promise?
- Yes. That is a promise.

40
00:04:06,373 --> 00:04:09,626
Like the promise of a road trip, too?

41
00:04:09,709 --> 00:04:11,044
Just you and me?

42
